Useful bitwise information.
---------------------------

to insert bits, use bitwise OR |
to disable bits, use bitwise AND &
to toggle bits, use bitwise XOR ^
to invert bits, use bitwise NOT ~
to read bit status, use bitwise AND & then shift to either left or right <<>>

Here are base 16 numbers in binary

0001 -> 1
0010 -> 2
0011 -> 3
0100 -> 4
0101 -> 5
0110 -> 6
0111 -> 7
1000 -> 8
1001 -> 9
1010 -> A
1100 -> B
1101 -> C
1110 -> D
1111 -> E
